People watch the immersive multimedia exhibition "I Aivazovsky" at Artplay Media in Moscow, Russia, on Nov. 28, 2020. The project "I Aivazovsky", combining a multimedia exhibition and a tv play, leads viewers through the life of the Russian painter Ivan Aivazovsky. (Photo by Maxim Chernavsky/Xinhua) 

